# Frontend Engineering (Next.js)

**Single app:** `apps/web/` — marketing + auth + dashboard.

## Route groups

| Group | Path | Rendering |
|-------|------|-----------|
| `(marketing)` | `/` | SSR/SSG sections |
| `(auth)` | `/login`, `/signup` | Client |
| `(dashboard)` | `/dashboard/**` | Client shell + pages |

## Rules

- Presentation only — business logic in NestJS (`apps/api`)
- Use `@genie/api-client` for API calls (replace mock store over time)
- Design system: `app/globals.css` tokens (indigo accent, neutral surfaces)
- Do not recreate `apps/dashboard` or `apps/marketing` — deprecated

## UI source

Dashboard UI ported from agentbloom-io reference. Extend via `features/dashboard/pages/` and `components/`.
